org.yamcs.xtce

Class BinaryDataEncoding

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yamcs.xtce.DataEncoding
      • org.yamcs.xtce.BinaryDataEncoding
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class BinaryDataEncoding
extends DataEncoding
    For binary data or for integer, float, string, or time data that is not in any of the known encoding formats. For any data that is not encoded in any of the known integer, float, string, or time data formats use a To/From transform algorithm. DIFFERS_FROM_XTCE: XTCE doesn't support LEADING_SIZE parameter types (it does only for strings). However it allows the size to be specified dynamically by the value of another parameter.
